PrecisAmendments to the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 which will permit the Minister of Natural Resources for Ontario to vary close times under the Aboriginal Communal Fishing Licences Regulations in respect of any species of fish caught in the inland waters of Ontario, for an indefinite period.
